reviewText: This arrived on time and it good condition. This show has 3 episodes, and it has cool WB commercials. The commercials are the same exact ones that were shown on Sat morning. I am very pleased with this show.

I don't know if I'll manage to see the entire series, but the third volume of "Viewtiful Joe" is much more interesting and funny than Vol. 2. This one's got "Pokemon"-like creatures that kids love, which can attach themselves to their brains and make them into devil children. I don't know, is the irony there plain enough? Anyway, yeah. That's really what goes on in this one.
